description: C3 Metals Inc. engages in the identification, acquisition, exploration, and evaluation of copper and gold deposits in Peru, Jamaica, and Canada. Its flagship property is the Jasperoide copper and gold project that consists of 49 claims covering an area of 267 square kilometers located in Southern Peru. The company was formerly known as Carube Copper Corp. and changed its name to C3 Metals Inc. in July 2020. C3 Metals Inc. is based in Toronto, Canada.
